-	 *    3 + (BITS_PER_LONG/8)*2 chars.
+	/*
+	 * Memory state around the buggy address:
+	 *  ff00ff00ff00ff00: 00 00 00 05 fe fe fe fe fe fe fe fe fe fe fe fe
+	 *  ...
+	 *
+	 * The length of ">ff00ff00ff00ff00: " is
